{"tid":512936,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"【紅色警戒】土耳其十日九夜遊記","createTime":"2017-12-29T04:40:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T09:00:43.000Z","uid":26445,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"3dd091d408486a99d8dcfb199ff845f197902afb","tid":512936,"uid":26445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T04:40:30.000Z","msg":"土耳其，一聽到就諗起就諗起火雞（兩者英文都係Turkey），由於我覺得成件事好九唔搭八，所以抱有強烈求知慾嘅我決定去一探究竟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，於是一趟探索火雞同土耳其有咩關係嘅旅程就展開了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n首先係到簡介下本次旅行嘅小小背景先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n <br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1.行程</span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n由30-Nov-2017至12-Dec-2017總共13日 (來回飛機各1日，但因為我返個程係分別係土耳其同荷蘭加埋Delay 成日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，所以總共搭飛機用咗3日，旅行10日。)<br />\n<br />\n<ins>10日旅行breakdown </ins><br />\n1/12 - 4/12 伊斯坦堡3日，3/12 棉堡1日(即日來回) <br />\n4/12 - 8/12卡帕多其亞5日(原本4日，之後決定留多日，後面會講 ) <br />\n8/12 - 9/12伊斯坦堡2日(原本3日 ) = 10日<br />\n*全部都係搭內陸機往返<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2.機票</span></ins></strong><br />\n <br />\n香港土耳其來回機票兩個麻甩佬，HK$8,642.00<br />\n香港&lt;-&gt;阿姆斯特丹 &ndash; 荷蘭皇家航空KLM<br />\n伊斯坦堡SAW機場&lt;-&gt;阿姆斯特丹 &ndash; 土耳其飛馬航空Pegasus + KLM<br />\n <br />\n<ins>內陸來回機票</ins><br />\n<br />\n即日來回，伊斯坦堡SAW機場&lt;-&gt;代尼茲利(棉堡) &ndash; Pegasus，兩個麻甩佬，HK$456.75<br />\n<br />\n3日來回，伊斯坦堡IST機場&lt;-&gt;內夫謝希爾(卡帕多其亞) &ndash; 土耳其航空Turkish Airlines，兩個麻甩佬兩個麻甩佬，HK$906.14<br />\n<br />\n單程機票，內夫謝希爾-&gt;伊斯坦堡SAW機場  &ndash; TA ，兩個麻甩佬，HK$508.03<br />\n(呢程其實可以避免，但係因為決定咗係卡帕多其亞留多1日，原定返伊斯坦堡個程機又改唔到期，所以要另外買多程返伊斯坦堡)<br />\n <br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3.酒店</span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n伊斯坦堡頭3晚 (1-Dec-2017至4-Dec-2017) <br />\nPierre Loti Hotel<br />\n地址：Piyerloti Cad. No: 1, Istanbul, 34400 Turkey<br />\n價錢：HK$1,431.51<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/29/112831_afc82b9c43516e9bc2543cc210f065cc.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F29%2F112831_afc82b9c43516e9bc2543cc210f065cc.JPG&h=6358df12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n卡帕多其亞3晚 + 1晚 (4-Dec-2017至8-Dec-2017)<br />\nGoreme Kaya Hotel<br />\n地址：Uzundere Cad. No. 43, Nevsehir, 50180 Turkey<br />\n價錢：HK$ 1,155.21 + TUY 210 (大約HK$ 430)    <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/29/113012_ad6ad1587d88490ecd894d7df42e9b8d.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F29%2F113012_ad6ad1587d88490ecd894d7df42e9b8d.JPG&h=7b6425b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n伊斯坦堡尾2晚 (8-Dec-2017至10-Dec-2017) - The Ambassador Hotel<br />\n地址：Ticarethane Cikmazi No 19, Istanbul, 34420 Turkey<br />\n價錢：HK$ 1,153.14<br />\n*原本3晚但我淨係住咗2晚，唔好問我點解<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/29/113430_1a3b9266b46bf9faca0754641028f302.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F29%2F113430_1a3b9266b46bf9faca0754641028f302.JPG&h=4eeb4a40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">4.洗費參考</span></ins></strong><br />\n呢個應該好多人會問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，我就應洗則洗無話平遊定蠔油，最後用咗HK$9,000.00到(唔連機票酒店!)，所以啲一定要洗嘅錢我打出嚟比大家參考下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">~HK$ 2 ： ~1 TL </span><br />\n<br />\n交通上：<br />\n<br />\n<ins>伊斯坦堡</ins><br />\n<br />\n伊斯坦堡Sabiha Gokcen機場(SAW)來回市區，正常會搭機場巴(土文：Ｈavatas，一出機場大馬路轉右就見到)，主要有兩車出去<br />\n<br />\n<ins>SAW&lt;&gt;Taksim</ins> (推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\nSAW &gt; Taksim 每日凌晨04:00 - 翌日凌晨01:00都有<br />\nTaksim &gt; SAW  每日凌晨03:30 - 翌日凌晨01:00都有<br />\n價錢：15TL<br />\n*到Taksim的話可以轉鐵路去酒店(以常見Sultanahmet嘅酒店為例，先搭Metro M2 Line去Vezneciler Istanbul U 再轉Tram Line T1去Sultanahmet，但營運時間係06:00-24:00，唔係你就焗搭的士)<br />\n<br />\n<ins>SAW&lt;&gt;Kadık&ouml;y</ins><br />\nSAW &gt; Kadık&ouml;y 每日凌晨04:00 - 翌日凌晨01:00都有<br />\nKadık&ouml;y &gt; SAW  每日凌晨04:15 - 翌日凌晨00:45都有<br />\n價錢：10TL<br />\n*呢條Line要去酒店區比較快但較麻煩(可以避免塞車，但一係轉船再轉鐵，一係搭鐵要狂轉線）<br />\n<br />\n打住咁多，因為返工忙應該出得慢，但有問題都可以係到問住我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddb2e1facd6fde8dad631623ca5d12afa0a4bda2","tid":512936,"uid":37237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T04:55:07.000Z","msg":"我都好想去留名睇路線"},{"pid":"cd631ecd5c71b078d673288b50ea98c3fc746f08","tid":512936,"uid":37237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T04:55:37.000Z","msg":"再留一個言<br />\n問定先 有無屌耳妹？"},{"pid":"2503e4aff7395bf53907e7e3cdf006a99bcf494a","tid":512936,"uid":26445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd631ecd5c71b078d673288b50ea98c3fc746f08","tid":512936,"uid":37237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T04:55:37.000Z","msg":"再留一個言<br />\n問定先 有無屌耳妹？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T05:04:35.000Z","msg":"1. 如果有well plan 同唔係天氣問題 其實可以試下去埋番紅花城安卡拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2. 無<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57b8d9a660a8e2e892781215bc33001b5d290807","tid":512936,"uid":32213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T05:07:13.000Z","msg":"樓主係大陸移民過來的吧？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22ab6bec9ad2b31680c6ec3f0acc5fe1be12aa89","tid":512936,"uid":26445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57b8d9a660a8e2e892781215bc33001b5d290807","tid":512936,"uid":32213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T05:07:13.000Z","msg":"樓主係大陸移民過來的吧？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T05:15:30.000Z","msg":"