23ea5d23b84b4a8f756bb80edbc6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F04%2F155406_8fee23ea5d23b84b4a8f756bb80edbc6.jpg&h=d55886bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n講完點樣係伊斯坦堡機場來回市區，咁伊斯坦堡市內嘅交通係點嘅呢?以下就講下。<br />\n<br />\n首先，你要買一張土耳其版嘅八達通，Istanbulkart，係伊斯坦堡鐵路任何一部黃色售票機都可以買，佢附近有張Instruction教你點樣買，咭6 TL一張（入面無錢），咭Limit 300TL，我去咗5日入50TL已經夠用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，而呢張咭可以用係巴士(不包括上述嘅機場巴士，機場巴士一定要上車之後買飛同渡輪，加上伊斯坦堡交通好方便，所以你基本上唔洗擔心交通咖啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n咭樣<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/04/164334_02e14bc6c830403f1bf0a2d6d3a5fd15.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F04%2F164334_02e14bc6c830403f1bf0a2d6d3a5fd15.JPG&h=88004dba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咭機<br />\n<img src=\"http://yofederico.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/C%C3%B3mo-adquirir-y-recargar-la-Istanbul-Kart-para-movernos-en-Estambul-01-750x563.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyofederico.com%2Fblog%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F07%2FC%25C3%25B3mo-adquirir-y-recargar-la-Istanbul-Kart-para-movernos-en-Estambul-01-750x563.jpg&h=342cdefc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e773661251ded68a5c4eab83d0b358d6d7299ba4","tid":512936,"uid":35620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T08:57:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e97eb32f6b855c93cb554333e953b7628434b51b","tid":512936,"uid":26445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e773661251ded68a5c4eab83d0b358d6d7299ba4","tid":512936,"uid":35620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T08:57:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T09:01:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmo