:26445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7835a64e5d81e33c40256608f79db9895863690","tid":512936,"uid":51268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f753b3eb5a8a2e8c9ab6dc90713a6024243f470","tid":512936,"uid":44377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T14:50:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一個女仔去危唔危險</blockquote>去棉堡同卡帕多其亞呢啲比較荒無嘅地方無個伴會無乜安全感 同埋去伊斯坦堡 安卡拉呢啲小心有恐襲 其實香港都對土耳其大部份地區有紅色旅遊警示  最好唔好</blockquote><br />\n土耳其男人好撚咸濕，唔係講笑<br />\n好聽d講叫熱情<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T15:17:01.000Z","msg":"土耳其妹熱唔熱情<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T00:39:17.000Z","msg":"係勁撚咸濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n土耳其妹好多個輪廓好標緻同對眼好靚 不過好似好保守<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30211e2dd4f53a6e9ce4e1621dc921bfeaafd1d5","tid":512936,"uid":26445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T09:51:22.000Z","msg":"咁伊斯坦堡嘅交通上係咁多喇，之後講下棉堡同卡帕多其亞嘅交通<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n首先你要去土耳其嘅其他地方，主要可以透過內陸機同跨區巴士(Otobus)到達，部份可以搭高鐵，但個啲唔係我schedule入面所以我都答你唔到。<br />\n<br />\n內陸機的話最好以伊斯坦堡為中心去plan，以我為例，因為要去埋棉堡同卡帕多其亞，而棉堡(代尼茲利機場)同卡帕多其亞(內夫謝希爾機場/開塞利機場)之間無直航機，而伊斯坦堡對呢兩點就有，所以我嘅旅程係伊斯坦堡&gt;棉堡&gt;伊斯坦堡&gt;卡帕多其亞&gt;伊斯坦堡咁去，每一程大約個半鐘，可以慳到時間，而且佢唔係好貴，來回機票係skyscanner買都係HK$400-500。<br />\n<br />\n不過你多時間、唔怕麻煩罨耷同想平的話，可以考慮下Otobus，HK$200有找，但個人唔建議。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>棉堡</ins></strong><br />\n究竟點去棉堡呢，<span style=\"color: red;\">我只會提供搭飛機嘅點去</span>，搭Otobus你就自己check check佢喇! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當你一出代尼茲利機場，你會見到好多牛牛一車車咁送入去，有好多隻流眼淚 佢地知就快俾人殺...真係好慘!<br />\n<br />\n牛牛係有靈性，幫人耤田....請大家唔好食牛! 我都已經開始戒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你會見到一埋白色Benz巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，上車同司機講你想去Pamukkale，佢會同你講係Denizli Otogar落車，好似15TL，1個鐘車程左右。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/05/172512_31ce0be30b4f7bb06f940a1157a08eae.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F05%2F172512_31ce0be30b4f7bb06f940a1157a08eae.JPG&h=1279854f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到咗Ｄenizli Ｏtogar，唔好咁心急，因為你未到咖，之後你要轉搭小巴(Dolums)號去Pamukkale，邊間公司不拘因為無咩方別，總之你問佢係咪到Pamukkale就得，10分鐘左右車程佢會係Pamukkale下面一個小鎮內店前放低你，咁你行去棉堡之前最好入去問一問啲店員你應該幾時係到搭返去Ｄenizli Otogar轉返去機場，咁你係棉堡嘅時間就會好就啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁之後你行上去就會見到棉堡了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"796a625b225b9d81afc8850c93c9ab38d892b6c7","tid":512936,"uid":26445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T03:16:14.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins>卡帕多其亞</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n最後講埋卡帕多其亞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，同樣我都係搭內陸機去，所以我只會係講點樣由內夫謝希爾機場機場去，而去卡帕多奇亞嘅機場有兩個：內夫謝希爾機場(NAV)同開塞利機場(ASR)，由於做過Research NAV係方便啲，所以建議大家係NAV去卡帕多其亞。<br />\n<br />\n當你落機行幾步就會出機場，會見到一堆白色Benz Van仔(Dolmus，同棉堡嗰種差唔多)，你同佢講你酒店叫咩同係邊個town，卡帕多其亞通常都係住 Goreme/Urgup，佢話ok嘅你就上車，直接送到你去酒店，無記錯15TL。<br />\n<br />\n當你要返機場你就同酒店講聲你邊班機，佢就會幫你book車，通常都係班機早一個鐘十五分鐘上車，但價錢好似同入城個時唔同；如果酒店幫唔到就行去啲小巴公司問；搭的士都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋係到提下你去到唔係伊斯坦堡嘅地方係用唔到Istanbulkart的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51f917bdd8974f359388c78fa82b3425db2c0469","tid":512936,"uid":33777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T04:19:37.000Z","msg":"得一篇仲要冇圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c34b885bf770afbebd28ffdd6d0df0cf46acf008","tid":512936,"uid":26445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T04:47:27.000Z","msg":"飲食上，其實主要睇下你平食定豪食，兩個人計平食的話70TL內有找，豪食就明above 100TL左右啦，我午餐同晚餐都豪食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比啲必食嘅大約價錢比大家參考下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n麵包：有好多種每間餐廳唔同，送嘅<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/09/124525_38d309d20762de4d12069cfcfc41b0d3.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F09%2F124525_38d309d20762de4d12069cfcfc41b0d3.JPG&h=99c646a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n扁豆湯 Lentil Soup <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：8TL - 15TL，正到瀨屎我每餐飲一碗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/09/122127_0e989fb054aaf6732360fa22faa6e7bc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F09%2F122127_0e989fb054aaf6732360fa22faa6e7bc.jpg&h=7fa20c23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咸酸奶 Ayran <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：2TL - 10TL，如果係餐廳自己沖會貴啲；包裝平啲<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/09/123052_d66012ec039ae4049e71bfc0cea7a762.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F09%2F123052_d66012ec039ae4049e71bfc0cea7a762.JPG&h=b902f482&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n烤肉 Kebab <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：40TL - 50TL，雞牛羊，雞最平羊最貴<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/09/123448_195c882d57cc987e1235ffa696e7c39d.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F09%2F123448_195c882d57cc987e1235ffa696e7c39d.JPG&h=571725e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n旋轉烤肉卷 Doner kebab <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：10TL - 15TL，泛指正宗土耳其烤肉，啫係用Pita卷起啲烤肉個隻；但有時會指用方包／麵包夾個種係德國烤肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/09/121903_0a441e57b248c62cbe33d8932d3db705.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F09%2F121903_0a441e57b248c62cbe33d8932d3db705.JPG&h=160e49fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陶罐燉肉 Testi Kebabi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：25TL - 40TL，源自卡帕多其亞，相傳係當年比羅馬帝國迫害嘅耶撚發明，方便保存同可以即時加熱食。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/09/123531_2574555378a602e923474545f712ba8d.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F09%2F123531_2574555378a602e923474545f712ba8d.JPG&h=dd37f50c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n茄子鑲肉 Karniyarik<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ：15TL-25TL<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/09/123702_44504d03986ba8feb78e3329f3b135c9.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F09%2F123702_44504d03986ba8feb78e3329f3b135c9.JPG&h=d1e7484b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實仲有好多，我會係遊記再說明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1147ceb843130c6df3c687df914e52deef7bebe5","tid":512936,"uid":26445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51f917bdd8974f359388c78fa82b3425db2c0469","tid":512936,"uid":33777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T04:19:37.000Z","msg":"得一篇仲要冇圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T04:48:27.000Z","msg":"出多篇飲食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}